Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.24,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繋がってる　確かなパス
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your power still flows into me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.42,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感じてる　大切なものをこの肩に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}きみとならFly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I decided to become a sage of the stars, oh like you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.26,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Push forward!! Pu- Push forward!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Flyin’ high!! Fl- Flyin’ high!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}止まる事ない二つのタイムライン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}変えていく　さあ二人でRight now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:09.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:14.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.41,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}無論發生什麼事 都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.95,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為我們是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.16,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我們是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.91,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}沒有人能阻　{擋}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.91,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(685,12)}挡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.54,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為我們是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.79,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}現在讓我們觸摸天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.04,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大樓不斷向前延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.26,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仰望狹窄的天空 閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:10.76,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下一刻 是更廣闊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.80,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要向前踏出一　 就能有全新的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:13.80,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(621,12)}步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.39,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我們不斷折返
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:16.72,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我們就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.52,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不忘初心 繼續前行!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:20.89,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}依靠　 飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:20.89,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(636,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.23,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}無論何地 我們都能將完美處理一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.69,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}時刻保持冷靜地管理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.36,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}飛離平凡的牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:29.40,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.90,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}洞察世界以此談判
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.66,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生活就是不斷地學習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.24,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直至死亡 都無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.00,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信我們的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.79,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那真實連結著的紐帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.58,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}　的力量依然流淌在我的體　{內}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.58,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(460,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.58,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(818,12)}内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.42,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能感受到 肩負著重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.92,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}與　一起飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.92,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(596,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.39,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我決定成為星之賢者 就如　一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.39,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(779,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.26,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}　　（向前推進!!向前推進!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.26,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(481,12)}噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.31,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}　　（飛向高空!!飛向高空!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.31,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(481,12)}噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.44,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兩條永不停止的時間線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:06.02,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}讓我們兩人一起改變 就是現在!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.52,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能為　做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.52,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(625,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.78,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能與　做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.78,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(625,12)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:09.86,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繼續前進！繼續前進!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:14.82,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}與　一起飛翔到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:14.82,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)\pos(522,12)}你
